{"tid":5033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我呀媽精神病再次發作","createTime":"2016-11-26T17:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T02:30:29.000Z","uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90dcf54f83900930c0d8d672edf5433b53c62a43","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"我呀媽呢排成日神神化化，<br />\n自言自語，琴日仲去澳門賭到無錢返香港<br />\n（好彩無借錢），<br />\n要我老豆救佢，我覺得面對住個精神病人好辛苦<br />\n叫佢食返藥，佢又話咩藥係魔，總知講埋d1999既野<br />\n搞到我要用粗暴既手法逼佢食，雖然好不孝<br />\n但都無辨法<br />\n<br />\nBtw講返小小背景先，我老母係14年前同11年前<br />\n都分別入過精神科住過一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣都係我呀婆逼佢入去，<br />\n但依家我呀婆身體有事，唔方便出手了<br />\n<br />\n加上公事同返學都有project要趕<br />\n點解個天要係我最忙果陣先玩鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我依家仲可以點做"},{"pid":"c9caaff64b56af7e4e5fd737033d04eedb52dec5","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:32:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6ab7927778859fad42138bdb06db88be6b3d81","tid":5033,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:34:31.000Z","msg":"雖然係仆街 <br />\n但更嚴重的事出現時<br />\n你要記住 你的人生係你的"},{"pid":"e12652672764c3417eb12aa263c9c227fe25f1da","tid":5033,"uid":5252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"唉，我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52b0e78f05cd8d8b17805037b9569811560dc3a","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:36:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然係仆街 <br />\n但更嚴重的事出現時<br />\n你要記住 你的人生係你的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我知...就快煩到我都有精神病"},{"pid":"f124dc2ba91f890d13dd2b09ce90380dba95b055","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉，我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你屋企人都有？"},{"pid":"2d58c9db398808cc67510c041b0e2646b16120fa","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c93be1242fbf2d6fc8a050b3e480a269cf32f6bd","tid":5033,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"巴打加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80b1f9928bd999324298af5570c71e4f73696c5","tid":5033,"uid":24187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:48:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8cf5033a37e02869791065e823e7b3127f3f5bc","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:49:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912e6172c47b4b52ade7b7806529b0d56a28300c","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:53:33.000Z","msg":"唉我老母依家又出夜街，又唔知去邊<br />\n又叫人咪跟住，其實精神病人個腦係點架<br />\n咁凍仲出街..."},{"pid":"01468328f81997921d9e9f99f6de660d0b47f6a7","tid":5033,"uid":5419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:55:48.000Z","msg":"巴打 皇天會祝福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa4663b278f93bd2414a22a41a61a2c3271043a","tid":5033,"uid":4612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T17:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 皇天會祝福你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但個天依家似玩鳩我多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2b06b376d2fb0567ef0b26a1db7f8a614c34f8","tid":5033,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"噴火仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8c2c7a44020d94277f9c07f5d2d5e634fd55f1","tid":5033,"uid":38842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"你媽咪情況都好嚴重。<br />\n有機會就報警送佢入院。<br />\n就算佢唔肯入，任何一個醫生都會覺得佢需要治療會向法官申請強制留院。<br />\n<br />\n有咩可以喺到問或者去我fb pm我(search 我個名就搵到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff8d2797f0322f8612f37133736a1832f2b411c0","tid":5033,"uid":37651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"講真,捉住佢又好、叫白車又好都要捉佢入院,要佢明白自己情況,如果到佢傷害到自己或者人地就太遲"},{"pid":"3e4b932d2706353f6b3b63f8f977b3097f886391","tid":5033,"uid":2114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你媽咪情況都好嚴重。<br />\n有機會就報警送佢入院。<br />\n就算佢唔肯入，任何一個醫生都會覺得佢需要治療會向法官申請強制留院。<br />\n<br />\n有咩可以喺到問或者去我fb pm我(search 我個名就搵到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有病咁多年啲insight都咁差<br />\n樓主應該都攪佢唔掂<br />\n入咗psy ward都應該要出form 7 <br />\n<br />\n但樓主都應該要同你阿爸夾計挾佢去急症<br />\n咩理由都好，少少病就帶佢去急症啦<br />\n急症多數都識做會收佢入院"},{"pid":"16eefc303ba702d809e0188726e44f4e3a7a6e21","tid":5033,"uid":44807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T02:30:29.000Z","msg":"我明，我兩個阿哥都有，感覺好似活係兩個世界，一個正常，一個失常咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}